room_title: Escape room "The Gallery" by Project Panic Austin in Austin
room_description: Vincent Ralph Quinn, an art collector turned artist, has recently passed away. His famous works took the world by storm, making him one of the richest men alive. You are invited to his private gallery where he has hidden a vast amount of his fortune. If you can solve his puzzles and uncover his secrets within the time limit then the money is yours! Will you prove that you are worthy of his inheritance?
